authorizeContract(address).details: authorize app contract to call into data contract

returns._0: A bool that is the current authorization status

broadcastData(uint256,uint256,uint256,ui.details: function for backend to broadcast technical state, store it in no1s1TechLogs, and modify the main state variable no1s1BatteryLevel (hourly?)

buy(uint256,address,string,uint256,uint2.details: buy function to access no1s1, returns QR code

checkAccess(bytes32,uint256,uint256).details: function triggered by backend to check whether QR code is valid and authorizes to unlock door

params._key: QR code detected by camera returns allowed duration to enter (if 0, door could stay locked)

checkActivity(bool,bytes32).details: function triggered by back-end shortly after access() function with sensor feedback (door openend, motion detected) if user has not entered, set occupancy back to not occupied and lock door

checkBuyStatus(uint256,uint256,uint256,u.details: retrieve values needed to buy meditation time

checkUserKey(bytes32).details: retrieve user information with key (QR code)

constructor.details: Constructor      Deploying the no1s1Data contract and the NFT contract for the no1s1 access token      The deploying account becomes contractOwner

deAuthorizeContract(address).details: deauthorize app contract to call into data contract

returns._0: A bool that is the current authorization status

exit(bool,uint256,bytes32).details: function triggered by backend after leaving no1s1. resets the occupancy state.

howAmI().details: Get operating status of no1s1 (main state variables)

howRichAmI().details: Get balance of no1s1 (without escrow paid)

returns._0: A bool that is the current operating status

no1s1InfoLog(uint256).details: function for backend to trigger storing the current state of no1s1 (daily)

refundEscrow(address,string,uint256).details: function triggered by user after leaving no1s1. Pays back escrow and sends out confirmation NFT.

setAccessabilityStatus(bool).details: function to modify the main state variable no1s1Accessability. This function is only for admins (not callable from app contract) to reset this state.

setOccupationStatus(bool).details: function to modify the main state variable no1s1Occupation. This function is only for admins (not callable from app contract) to reset this state in case exiting the space is not detected

setOperatingStatus(bool).details: Sets contract operations on/off When operational mode is disabled, all write transactions except for this one will fail
